narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: This class is a great introductory English class. The professor is helpful, the topic is interesting, and the breadth of material is great. The books you read are manageable and the papers are fun to write. I would recommend this class to anyone looking for an intro english class in which they can write 5 good papers to learn how to write better.
Yes, take the class. The syllabus and teacher definitely make ENGL 115 worth taking.
Yes absolutely! Great intro English class!
I would recommend this course for someone looking for an English class that is a good balance of reading and writing and a workload that is significant but manageable.
